Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:51.89,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}Môj pohľad bol vždy upretý na teba
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:58.13,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kimi ga suki de
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.95,0:21:58.13,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}Mám ťa rád
