Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:04.54,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}Vždy som ťa mal rád
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:10.94,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kono omoi koi demo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.46,0:22:10.94,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}Nevadí mi, ak tento pocit je to, čomu hovoria láska,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:14.24,Ed - R,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}kizu tsuitemo ii
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.20,0:22:14.24,Ed - E,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)\be1\blur3}A je mi jedno, ak ma zraní
